### Get all sermons
GET http://localhost:8000/api/sermons

### Get a sermon by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/sermons/1

### Create a new sermon
POST http://localhost:8000/api/sermons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sample Sermon",
  "preacher": "John Doe",
  "date": "2025-06-22",
  "description": "A sample sermon description.",
  "audioUrl": "http://example.com/audio.mp3"
}

### Update a sermon
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/sermons/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Sermon Title"
}

### Delete a sermon
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/sermons/1

